title: ECW's Beulah McGilligcutty in: DayDreaming
description:
ECW&#039;s Beulah McGillicutty is one of pro wrestling&#039;s most infamous divas. You see, she wasn&#039;t just the girlfriend of Raven and Tommy Dreamer in ECW... She was an adult film actress as well!

Now, for the first time ever, find out what a sexy wrestling diva Day Dreams about as she dances around and makes many wrestling fans&#039; dreams, or prayers, come true!

This film is NOT for the weak of heart and should only be viewed by those over 18 years of age.
